{"id":531829,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/06/【图说天朝】面对百姓-武警部队真心谋打仗/","date":"2016-06-08T08:46:29Z","modified":"2016-06-08T08:51:48Z","title":"【图说天朝】面对百姓 武警部队真心谋打仗","content":"<blockquote><p>北风 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/wenyunchao/status/740214447772426240\" target=\"_blank\">@wenyunchao</a>：武警山东省总队“卫士-16”演习实施方案。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/006lS5jQgw1f4n4jf4yh4j30zk0qodp0.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-531836\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/006lS5jQgw1f4n4jf4yh4j30zk0qodp0.jpg\" alt=\"006lS5jQgw1f4n4jf4yh4j30zk0qodp0\" width=\"585\" height=\"439\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/006lS5jQgw1f4n4jf4yh4j30zk0qodp0.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/006lS5jQgw1f4n4jf4yh4j30zk0qodp0-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/006lS5jQgw1f4n4jf4yh4j30zk0qodp0-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://news.qq.com/a/20160531/008267.htm\" target=\"_blank\">新华社｜31省武警部队举行大型演习：数十万人上万辆车参加</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>“在这次演习中，某部演练情况设想与实战差距较大，某指挥员不善于因时因地运用战法手段，某部实兵参演率偏低……”29日下午，随着一场直指问题的反思式总结在武警部队作战指挥中心举行，武警部队“卫士－16”首长机关带部分实兵演习划上了一个充满硝烟味的句号。分布在全国31个省区市的3万余名各级指挥员通过电视电话会议系统全面回顾演习得失，深刻认识自身差距，纷纷表示，要巩固演习成果、用更细更实更严的标准大力推进实战化训练。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>武警天津总队“卫士—16”演习视频截图</strong>（<a href=\"http://www.js7tv.cn/video/201605_47291.html\" target=\"_blank\">链接</a>）：</p>\n<blockquote><p>发布时间：2016年5月30日</p>\n<p>近日，武警天津总队组织了一场名为“卫士—16”的实战演练。演练中演习导演部提前20个小时拉响了战斗警报，支队立即启动了应急预案，不到20分钟全部人员已经登车完毕向目标区域机动。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习1-e1465372940466.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-531830\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习1-e1465372940466.jpg\" width=\"535\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习1-e1465372940466.jpg 4384w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习1-e1465372940466-300x170.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习1-e1465372940466-768x434.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习1-e1465372940466-1024x579.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习2-e1465372902283.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-531831\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习2-e1465372902283.jpg\" width=\"535\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习2-e1465372902283.jpg 4394w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习2-e1465372902283-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习2-e1465372902283-768x431.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习2-e1465372902283-1024x575.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习3-e1465372980167.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-531832\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习3-e1465372980167.jpg\" width=\"535\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习3-e1465372980167.jpg 4405w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习3-e1465372980167-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习3-e1465372980167-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习3-e1465372980167-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习4-e1465373020863.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-531833\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习4-e1465373020863.jpg\" width=\"535\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/武警演习4-e1465373020